      • updateCustomValue

        protected void updateCustomValue(SingleObjectiveExperimentTask.Result result)
        This method return a partial result that can be a instance of the final result list.

        Updates the customValue property. Calls to updateCustomValueProperty are coalesced and run later on the FX application thread, so calls to updateCustomValueProperty, even from the FX Application thread, may not necessarily result in immediate updates to this property, and intermediate message values may be coalesced to save on event notifications.

        This method is safe to be called from any thread.

        Parameters:
        result - is a parcial result of the total solution
